DIGEST
SB 350 Original 2026 Regular Session Cathey
Present law requires the Louisiana Soybean Association to submit the names of five practical
soybean producers to the governor, who must appoint three members to serve on the
Louisiana Soybean and Grain Research and Promotion Board.
Proposed law retains present law but changes the name of the "Louisiana Soybean
Association" to the "Louisiana Cotton and Grain Association".
Effective August 1, 2026.
(Amends R.S. 3:3552(A))
